No, no, Fighting is not the Vice of theſe Times;
and as for a little Swaggering—damn it, I can do it as
well as the beſt of 'em.

O, Sir! My Paſſion has undone me—I am diſcover'd;
it is my Husband, Sir George, and he is
looking for me—

Lord, Sir!—he is the moſt paſſionate of Mortals;
and I am afraid is in Liquor too—and then he
is mad.
